						<div class="postbody">You can do some FM with pitch modulation (assuming we speak of sine waves). However, it takes two channels to use, and it has a limited range on how the pitch is affected (up to I believe an octave). Plus, only ADSR and gain values affect the strength of the modulation, not the actual volume.</div>

